## 3. `app/` (App Router)

Holds **routing only**. No business logic, no GSAP, no atmosphere code.

```
app/
в”њв”Ђ layout.tsx               # Root layout: <html>, <body>, providers, global atmosphere shell
в”њв”Ђ page.tsx                 # Home page: composes chapters
в”њв”Ђ globals.css              # @theme tokens, base resets, Lenis-friendly defaults
в”њв”Ђ providers.tsx            # CursorProvider, LenisProvider, TransitionDirector, MotionConfig
в”њв”Ђ template.tsx             # Optional: per-route mount/unmount transitions
в”њв”Ђ (chapters)/              # Route group for narrative pages
в”‚  в”њв”Ђ work/
в”‚  в”‚  в”њв”Ђ page.tsx
в”‚  в”‚  в””в”Ђ [slug]/page.tsx    # Case study detail
в”‚  в”њв”Ђ studio/page.tsx       # Human chapter (about / philosophy)
в”‚  в””в”Ђ contact/page.tsx
в””в”Ђ not-found.tsx
```

### Constraints
- Pages declaratively compose `<XChapter>` components and `<ChapterSeam>` between them.
- No raw `<h1>`, `<section>`, `<div>` for layout in pages вЂ” only chapter components.
- `layout.tsx` handles fonts, providers, and the root `<WebGLRoot>` and `<CustomCursor>`.

