## 6. `hooks/`

Cross-cutting React hooks (when not domain-specific to `lib/`).

```
hooks/
в”њв”Ђ useReducedMotion.ts
в”њв”Ђ useBreakpoint.ts
в”њв”Ђ useIsTouch.ts
в”њв”Ђ useScrollProgress.ts
в”њв”Ђ useLenisScroll.ts
в””в”Ђ useGsapContext.ts
```

### Constraints
- Hook files: one hook per file. Default export is the hook function.
- Hook names: always `useX`. Always TypeScript.
- Avoid hooks that wrap a single line of state вЂ” prefer inline.

